Class Duck

java.lang.Object
Inheritance.Bird
Inheritance.Waterfowl
Inheritance.Duck
public class Duck extends Waterfowl
The Duck class is a subclass of Waterfowl. It represents a duck with specific properties such as breed, plumage pattern, and pattern color.
